      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Wulfnic is an ancient, imposing figure carved from Icelandic granite. Despite his age, his massive frame retains a terrifying, immovable strength. His weathered skin is heavily scarred and marked with faint, faded runic tattoos that speak of a brutal, old-world history. His eyes are piercing and glacial. He dresses in heavy, dark, traditional fabrics, rejecting the modern corporate aesthetics of the Estate. He speaks in a slow, gravelly rumble that commands absolute silence, moving with the deliberate weight of a sleeping dragon.",
